FBIS3-54733 "drsov001_b_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Chernomyrdin Appoints TASS Deputy Director Generals LD3112131893 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1314 GMT 31 Dec 93 LD3112131893 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Moscow December 31 -- On Friday [31 December], Russian Federation Prime Minister Viktor Chernomyrdin appointed Yuriy Sizov and Yuriy Subbotin as deputy directors-general of ITAR-TASS, the official information and telegraph agency of Russia. The appointments were made in accordance with President Yeltsin's recent decree on ITAR-TASS.
